    </div>
    <div class="modal-body">
      <div class="council-dropzone" id="council-dz"
           ondragover="event.preventDefault();this.classList.add('drag-over')"
           ondragleave="this.classList.remove('drag-over')"
           ondrop="handleCouncilDrop(event)">
        <div class="council-dropzone-title">⬇ DROP BUSINESS BRIEF · PDF · RULES · MODEL</div>
        <div class="council-dropzone-sub">Drop files or URLs here — Claude runs 4-perspective critique<br>Technical QA · ROI Strategist · Infrastructure Architect · Risk Analyst</div>
